namic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/295907/', '[1] "Product Information. Iopidine (apraclonidine ophthalmic)." Alcon Laboratories Inc[2] "Product Information. Alphagan (brimonidine ophthalmic)." Allergan Inc  (2001):[3] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[4] Pekdemir M, Yanturali S, Karakus G "More than just an ocular solution." Emerg Med J 22 (2005):  753-4[5] "Product Information. Mirvaso (brimonidine topical)." Galderma Laboratories Inc  (2013):', 1767365210);
